ny preferred hard and soft skills. Example Cleaner requirements High school diploma or equivalent required Minimum 1 year experience in cleaning Reliable, punctual and responsible worker Requires bending, reaching and lifting a minimum of 25 lbs Ability to walk or stand for long hours Flexibility to work overtime when necessary Cleaner related job titles: Heavy Cleaner Cleaning Specialist Janitorial Cleaner General Cleaner Night Cleaner Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
